title: Beachbody Body Gospel Workout System
description: At last, you can combine the power of your faith with your desire to lose weight and get fit. Body Gospel is a first-of-its-kind programme that includes workouts set to inspirational gospel music, breakthrough new resistance bands, and a complete nutrition plan created by fitness icon Donna Richardson Joyner. She shows you how to combine this effective programme with your faith in God to transform your body and your life. With glorious music guaranteed to get you moving, every workout is a "party with a purpose", and the results will amaze you. If you believe, you will succeed! Whether you have 40, 30, 20, or just 10 minutes, Body Gospel gives you uplifting workouts set to foot-stomping gospel hits. Anyone--from beginner to advanced--can do these workouts and see results
